    "This Consensus View, which is the outcome of discussions at the Recognizing Preprint Peer Review workshop [16], provides recommendations to empower researchers to provide open and constructive peer review for preprints, and issues a call to action to stakeholders in the community to accelerate the growing momentum of preprint sharing."
  ]
}